            <h2>HEY FRIENDS!</h2>
            <p>Opening a bookstore has always been my dream, just not one I thought I’d actually achieve. But here I am, and I am so thankful for it!</p>
            <p><strong>Self Wise®</strong> is a bold attempt to avoid piling up more student debt in a challenging economy, while still building a meaningful career I love. In the “unprecedented event of our lifetime” #53 (or #54? I’ve lost count), it just made sense to invest a semester’s tuition in creating my own path—one that doesn’t feel like selling my soul to The Man. So far, it feels like a pretty decent payoff!</p>
            <p>I have BIG goals for Self Wise, including a cozy storefront (coffee bar included, of course), a book club (buddy reads, anyone?), in-house designed bookish merch, and maybe even Special Edition books or curated book boxes.</p>
            <p>Every purchase you make brings Self Wise® closer to achieving all of this—and maybe even more than I’ve imagined.</p>
            <p>Thank you for supporting a small business and my dreams.</p>
            <p>— Lex x</p>
